title: twenty
description:
20 tenÂ´s was compiled from the perfect UCI vids which appeared right after this tour

It contains the best Â´Â´specialÂ´Â´ performances, songs which were rarely performed or performed in a different manner. All thanks to UCI and the original recorders, this compilation was made by a friend for private use but I think itÂ´s worth sharing.

Torrent will be up as long as there are seeders

Songs peformed

** Controversy (Antwerp). Included because of the intro

** Empty Room (Herning). No explanation needed, rare song, perfect HQ video

** Stratus (Herning). At the time it was a rarity but this performance wit Sheila E is still special

** Future Soul Song (Copenhagen). Same

** We Party Hearty/ Which Way is Up (Arnhem ''pre-show''). Was included for the intro to 2nd song which is probably funkiest moment on the whole Tour!

** The Love We Make, highlight of probably the best show of the tour

** Shh (Arnhem); she's probably STILL speechless....

** Crimson and Clover (Berlin). just because it will probably never be played anymore

** Forever In My Life/ Act Of God. Half a year after the release a much better version of this show appeared but this is still an absolute stunner. Act of God is a an absolute rarity, probably the only time it was played live EVER. Hunt down the final Berlin video for the perfect version

**Dreamer (Antwerp). One of those songs nobody cared about at the time but listening now it's brilliant

** I feel For You/ A Love Bizarre. Not rare at all but Prince has hardly ever been THIS relaxed on stage before and after. Nice inclusion

** Peach (Rome). Included for the HQ and the brilliant mocking of Keith Richards' guitar playing and a testament to his playing songs long after half of the stadium has left, and to show contrast to the other side of his performance spectrum :

** Sometimes It Snows in April (Bergen). Pure. Simple. Genius

** Beautiful Strange/Miss You (Paris).

** ''Bonus''
